'''异氰酸'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，分子式为HNCO，通常写作 H–N=C=O。它是无色的物质，有挥发性，[[有毒|有毒]]，[[沸点|沸点]]为 23.5 °C。為[[氰酸|氰酸]]的[[互變異構體|互變異構體]]。

异氰酸对应的[[阴离子|阴离子]] {{chem|[N{{=}}C{{=}}O]|-}} 和氰酸一样，也被称作[[氰酸盐|氰酸盐]]。相关的[[官能团|官能团]] –N=C=O 叫做[[异氰酸酯|异氰酸酯]]，是{{le|氰酸酯|Cyanate ester}} –O–C≡N、[[雷酸盐|雷酸盐]] –O–N<sup>+</sup>≡C<sup>−</sup>和{{le|氧化腈|nitrile oxide}} –C≡N<sup>+</sup>–O<sup>−</sup>的异构体。<ref name=mart2019/>

异氰酸于 1830年被[[尤斯图斯·冯·李比希|尤斯图斯·冯·李比希]]和[[弗里德里希·维勒|弗里德里希·维勒]]发现。<ref>{{cite journal | title = Untersuchungen über die Cyansäuren | author = Liebig, J. | author2 = Wöhler, F. | journal = Ann. Phys. | volume = 20 | issue = 11 | pages = 394 | year = 1830 | url = http://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k15105c/f377.table | doi = 10.1002/andp.18300961102 | bibcode = 1830AnP....96..369L | access-date = 2021-03-28 | archive-date = 2018-08-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180806150152/https://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k15105c/f377.table | dead-url = no }}</ref>  

异氰酸是含有[[碳|碳]]、[[氢|氢]]、[[氮|氮]]和[[氧|氧]]这四个在[[有机化学|有机化学]]和生物学中最常见的原子组成的稳定分子里，最简单的。它也是四个[[化学式|化学式]]为 HOCN 的化合物中唯一稳定的，其它三个是[[氰酸|氰酸]] H–O–C≡N 、[[雷酸|雷酸]] H–C≡N<sup>+</sup>–O<sup>−</sup><ref>{{cite journal | title = Fulminic Acid in the History of Organic Chemistry | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-chemical-education_2000-07_77_7/page/851 | author = Kurzer, Frederick | year = 2000 | journal = Journal of Chemical Education | volume = 77 | issue = 7 | pages = 851–857 | doi = 10.1021/ed077p851|bibcode = 2000JChEd..77..851K }}</ref>和{{le|异雷酸|isofulminic acid}} H–O–N<sup>+</sup>≡C<sup>−</sup>。<ref name=mart2019>William R. Martin and David W. Ball (2019): "Small organic fulminates as high energy materials. Fulminates of acetylene, ethylene, and allene". ''Journal of Energetic Materials'', volume 31, issue 7, pages 70-79. {{doi|10.1080/07370652.2018.1531089}}</ref><ref name=quan2010>Donghui Quan, Eric Herbst, Yoshihiro Osamura, and Evelyne Roueff (2010): "Gas-grain modeling of isocyanic acid (HNCO), cyanic acid (HOCN), fulminic acid (HCNO), and isofulminic acid (HONC) in assorted interstellar environments" ''The Astrophysical Journal'', volume 725, issue 2, pages {{doi|10.1088/0004-637X/725/2/2101}}</ref>

==结构==
尽管根据[[价键理论|价键理论]]，异氰酸可以被写成 HN=C=O，气态[[红外光谱|红外光谱]]显示 2268.8 cm<sup>−1</sup>的震动，由碳-氮三键引起。<ref>Nakamoto, part A, p 190</ref><ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1002/cber.19891220425 | volume=122 | title=The CHNO Isomers | journal=Chemische Berichte | year=1989 | pages=753–766| last1=Teles | first1=Joaquim Henrique | last2=Maier | first2=Günther | last3=Andes Hess | first3=B. | last4=Schaad | first4=Lawrence J. | last5=Winnewisser | first5=Manfred | last6=Winnewisser | first6=Brenda P. | issue=4 }}</ref>因此， H{{overset|+|N}}≡C−O<sup>−</sup> 才是主要的[[共振_(化学)|共振异构体]]。

==性质==
===物理性质===
纯异氰酸的[[熔点|熔点]]为 −86.8 °C ，[[沸点|沸点]]为 23.5 °C，所以在常温下有挥发性。<ref name = nco>Greenwood, p323</ref><ref>Wells, p 722</ref>

===酸性===
在水溶液下，异氰酸是一种[[弱酸|弱酸]]，[[酸度系数|p''K''<sub>a</sub>]]为 3.7：<ref name=scdb>[http://www.acadsoft.co.uk/scdbase/scdbase.htm IUPAC SC-Database] {{Wayback|url=http://www.acadsoft.co.uk/scdbase/scdbase.htm |date=20170619235720 }} A comprehensive database of published data on equilibrium constants of metal complexes and ligands</ref>
:HNCO {{eqm}} H<sup>+</sup> + NCO<sup>−</sup>

===水解===
异氰酸[[水解|水解]]成[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]和[[氨|氨]]：

: HNCO +  H<sub>2</sub>O   →   CO<sub>2</sub>  +   NH<sub>3</sub>

===聚合反应===
在高浓度下，异氰酸会聚合成[[三聚体|三聚体]][[三聚氰酸|三聚氰酸]]和{{le|1,3,5-三亚胺基-2,4,6-三氧六环|cyamelide}}，一种聚合物。它们可以简单地从液态或气态反应物中分离。三聚氰酸加热时会分解成异氰酸。<ref name=nco/> 

===在溶液里的稳定性===
稀异氰酸在惰性[[溶液|溶液]]中稳定，例如[[醚|醚]]和[[氯代烃|氯代烃]]。<ref name=eEROS>A. S. Narula, K. Ramachandran “Isocyanic Acid” in Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis, 2001, John Wiley & Sons, New York. {{DOI|10.1002/047084289X.ri072m}} Article Online Posting Date: April 15, 2001.</ref>

===反应===
异氰酸和[[胺|胺]]反应，形成[[脲|脲]]（碳酰胺）：
:HNCO  +  RNH<sub>2</sub>   →  RNHC(O)NH<sub>2</sub>.
这个反应叫做'''碳酰胺化反应'''。

===互变异构===
{{see also|氰酸}}
异氰酸有一个[[互变异构体|互变异构体]]——氰酸 HOCN，其中氧原子（而不是异氰酸的氮原子）与氢原子连接。它对分解不稳定，但在溶液中和异氰酸形成平衡，有3%的异氰酸以氰酸形式存在。振动光谱表明氮和碳原子之间存在[[三键|三键]]。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Teles|first=Joaquim Henrique|author2=Maier, Günther |author3=Andes Hess, B. |author4=Schaad, Lawrence J. |author5=Winnewisser, Manfred |author6=Winnewisser, Brenda P. |year=1989|title=The CHNO Isomers|journal=Chem. Ber.|volume=122|issue=4|pages=1099–0682|doi= 10.1002/cber.19891220425}}</ref>

低温[[光解|光解]]含有HNCO的固体可以产生氰酸 H-O-C≡N。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Jacox, M.E. |author2=Milligan, D.E. | title = Low-Temperature Infrared Study of Intermediates in the Photolysis of HNCO and DNCO  | journal = Journal of Chemical Physics | year = 1964 | volume = 40 | issue = 9 | pages = 2457–2460 | doi = 10.1063/1.1725546|bibcode = 1964JChPh..40.2457J }}</ref>人们尚未分离出纯氰酸，而异氰酸是所有溶剂中的主要存在形式。<ref name=eEROS/>

==制备==
异氰酸可以由[[氰酸盐|氰酸盐]]，例如[[氰酸钾|氰酸钾]]和气态[[氯化氢|氯化氢]]或是像[[草酸|草酸]]之类的酸反应而成。<ref>{{cite journal | title = Synthesis, Properties and Dimerization Study of Isocyanic Acid | author1 = Fischer, G. | author2 = Geith, J. | author3 = Klapötke, T. M. | author4 = Krumm B. | journal = Z. Naturforsch. | year = 2002 | volume = 57b | issue = 1 | pages = 19–25 | doi = 10.1515/znb-2002-0103 | s2cid = 37461221 | url = http://www.znaturforsch.com/ab/v57b/s57b0019.pdf | access-date = 2021-03-29 | archive-date = 2012-02-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120205210926/http://www.znaturforsch.com/ab/v57b/s57b0019.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>

: H<sup>+</sup>  +  NCO<sup><big><big>-</big></big></sup>  →  HNCO

HNCO 也可以由三聚体[[三聚氰酸|三聚氰酸]]热分解而成：

: C<sub>3</sub>H<sub>3</sub>N<sub>3</sub>O<sub>3</sub>  →  3 HNCO

[[弗里德里希·维勒|弗里德里希·维勒]]合成[[尿素|尿素]]的逆反应：
:OC(NH<sub>2</sub>)<sub>2</sub> → HNCO + NH<sub>3</sub>
其中的异氰酸会迅速聚合成三聚氰酸。

==存在==
异氰酸在[[星际物质|星际物质]]中被检测到。<ref name=quan2010/>

异氰酸也在多种[[烟|烟]]中用[[质谱法|质谱法]]被检测到，包括[[烟雾|烟雾]]和{{le|烟气|cigarette smoke}}。异氰酸易溶于[[水|水]]，会对肺部构成健康风险。<ref>{{cite web|last=Preidt|first=Robert|title=Chemical in Smoke May Pose Health Risk|url=http://www.accuweather.com/blogs/health/respiratory/50653/chemical-in-smoke-may-pose-hea.asp|work=MyOptumHealth|publisher=AccuWeather|access-date=14 September 2011|archive-date=2011-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111121045533/http://www.accuweather.com/blogs/health/respiratory/50653/chemical-in-smoke-may-pose-hea.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>

